OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FThe Los Angeles Marathon has come
OL,8,Funder scrutiny after organisers
OL,9,Fallowed racers to stop at an earlier
OL,10,Ffinish line and still receive a
OL,11,Ffinisher's medal.
OL,13,FThose participating in this year's
OL,14,Frace, which took place on March 8,
OL,15,Fwere given the option to stop at mile
OL,16,F18, instead of the usual 26.2-mile
OL,17,Ffinish, amid higher-than-average
OL,18,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FThe McCourt Foundation, which hosts
OL,8,Fthe event, said on its website last
OL,9,Fweek: "If you're having a tough day,
OL,10,Fyou can choose to take the turn at
OL,11,Fmile 18 and head into the finish line
OL,12,Fearly."
OL,14,FIt also encouraged runners to prepare
OL,15,Fas best as they could for the weather,
OL,16,Fadding that "there is no shame in
OL,17,Fmaking a smart decision for your body".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FTemperatures reached 32 celesuis in
OL,8,FLos Angeles on Sunday, according to
OL,9,FAccuWeather. The average temperature
OL,10,Ffor LA in March is 21 celesuis.
OL,12,FThose who crossed the finish line at
OL,13,Fmile 18 received "a finisher medal and
OL,14,Fany respective challenge medal".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FMeg Treat, spokesperson for the 2026
OL,8,FLA Marathon, told Runner's World that
OL,9,Fthey have frequent weather
OL,10,Fconversations, adding: "We start
OL,11,Factively monitoring it with the LA
OL,12,FFire Department, who partners with the
OL,13,FNational Weather Service ten days
OL,14,Fbefore the race."
OL,16,FThe McCourt Foundation said the mile
OL,17,F18 option was only available for last
OL,18,FSunday's event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
