CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FThe news received a mixed reaction
OL,8,Fonline, with some embracing the change
OL,9,Fas a necessary safety measure while
OL,10,Fothers disagreed with the decision.
OL,12,FOne user on TikTok said: "You've been
OL,13,Ftraining for it, please go ahead, do
OL,14,Fit, if you feel you need to cut it,
OL,15,Fthat is okay."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FAn X user said: "Smart of LA Marathon
OL,8,Fprotecting runners. As RD runner
OL,9,Fsafety is paramount." But they added:
OL,10,F"I certainly wouldn't accept a
OL,11,Fmarathon medal after running 18mi
OL,12,Fthough. Whatever happened to the DNF?"
OL,14,FLisa Cusack, a Republican official in
OL,15,FLos Angeles, posted on social media:
OL,16,F"People who don't finish the Marathon
OL,17,Fcan identify as people who do finish
OL,18,Fthe Marathon."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773162680
OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FAfter hearing about the mile-18
OL,8,Foption, one user on X said: " If you
OL,9,Fhaven't run a marathon, you wouldn't
OL,10,Funderstand why 18 miles is the number
OL,11,Fthey chose.
OL,13,F"Why not 16 or 20? Because mile 18 is
OL,14,Fwhen it gets hard.
OL,16,F"Miles 18-23 are the hardest. It's
OL,17,Fsuch a slap in the face to finishers
OL,18,Fwhen these folks get a medal for
OL,19,Fdropping out. Pathetic."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
