OL,3,CLos Angeles Marathon gives finisher
OL,4,Cmedals to runners who stopped at mile
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FAnother X user said, "A marathon is 26
OL,8,Fmiles. If you only run 18, you aren't
OL,9,Fa 'finisher'."
OL,11,FITV News has contacted the McCourt
OL,12,FFoundation for comment.
